            Published 11:05 a.m. ET Sept. 15, 2016 | Updated 10:21 a.m. ET Sept. 16, 2016Technology executive Tony Prophet has been appointed chief equality officer at Salesforce.com(Photo: Jack Gruber, USA TODAY)
            
